{"tid":1629190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"星期二係咪應該發動三罷","createTime":"2019-10-06T07:16:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T11:29:52.000Z","uid":201605,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4121c11c130cccc981fd7329d9204be041596824","tid":1629190,"uid":201605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:16:16.000Z","msg":"政府選擇係星期五行緊急法，係知道香港人善忘，只會嬲一兩日，等你三日假期用晒力。<br />\n就算全市停工，都只係假期，對社會影響唔大，變相俾時間星期二正常返工返學<br />\n更加有藉口話用緊急法成功「止暴制亂」<br />\n緊急法開咗頭，就會變本加厲，已經有消息話會用緊急法將拘留時間延長至96小時。<br />\n係咪應該係變本加厲前黎多鋪三罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等外國人知我哋仲反緊緊急法，幫助國際戰線"},{"pid":"54bdb4485991173d858ba5e68783140338df32c9","tid":1629190,"uid":239453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:17:08.000Z","msg":"[國際文宣] 話你知 屙緊屎個陣 你可以做啲乜??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629172\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629172</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"79064be731682c25ccf5df518281abf296e2a2dc","tid":1629190,"uid":57513,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:19:20.000Z","msg":"地鐵停駛=協助三罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"365f0b0b3720f19590d53b9dd340e74ee9c55fb2","tid":1629190,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"79064be731682c25ccf5df518281abf296e2a2dc","tid":1629190,"uid":57513,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:19:20.000Z","msg":"地鐵停駛=協助三罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T07:25:13.000Z","msg":"工作日就開返架啦"},{"pid":"6603b213661b3378cd80048df5807b64d8006780","tid":1629190,"uid":322508,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"365f0b0b3720f19590d53b9dd340e74ee9c55fb2","tid":1629190,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"79064be731682